OL,3,CBrain tumour patient praises Jersey's
OL,4,Cresponse to Blue Islands' collapse
OL,6,FA Jersey resident who needs an urgent
OL,7,Foperation for a brain tumour has
OL,8,Fpraised the island's health department
OL,9,Ffor their quick response to Blue
OL,10,FIslands' collapse.
OL,12,FKayla O'Brien has a meningioma, which
OL,13,Fis a tumour that grows from the
OL,14,Fmembranes around the brain and spinal
OL,15,Fcord.
OL,17,FShe was due to fly to Southampton with
OL,18,FBlue Islands this coming Sunday for
OL,19,Fessential surgery to have it removed -
OL,20,Fbefore the airline announced it was
OL,21,Fcancelling all future flights.
