OL,3,CBrain tumour patient praises Jersey's
OL,4,Cresponse to Blue Islands' collapse
OL,6,FKayla contacted Jersey's health team
OL,7,Fon Saturday to ask how she would be
OL,8,Fable to get to the UK and says the
OL,9,Fspeed of their response was very
OL,10,Fcomforting.
OL,12,FShe adds: "I dropped them a line
OL,13,Fsaying, 'Don't think about me as I
OL,14,Fwasn't meant to fly for another seven
OL,15,Fdays, but I'd love to hear what you're
OL,16,Fplanning'.
OL,18,F"They got back to me within 20
OL,19,Fminutes, and told me that I'd have my
OL,20,Fflight rebooked by 4pm on Monday.
