OL,3,CBrain tumour patient praises Jersey's
OL,4,Cresponse to Blue Islands' collapse
OL,6,F"It was really reassuring to know that
OL,7,Feverything is going forward."
OL,9,FEarly on Saturday morning, Loganair
OL,10,Fannounced that it would be operating
OL,11,F'rescue' flights to and from Jersey
OL,12,Fand Southampton, ensuring the key
OL,13,Froute for UK medical treatment would
OL,14,Fremain operational.
OL,16,FThe Scottish airline has since
OL,17,Fadvertised this service, along with
OL,18,Froutes between Jersey and Guernsey,
OL,19,FExeter and Bristol, into the New Year.
