OL,3,CBrain tumour patient praises Jersey's
OL,4,Cresponse to Blue Islands' collapse
OL,6,FKayla has been told that she will be
OL,7,Frebooked on a flight to Southampton
OL,8,Fbefore her operation, which is
OL,9,Fexpected to be provided by Loganair.
OL,11,FShe says: "It meant a lot.
OL,13,F"Living with a brain tumour is quite
OL,14,Fan up and down experience anyway, and
OL,15,Fhaving that bit of assurance was one
OL,16,Fless thing to worry about.
OL,18,F"It was handled really efficiently;
OL,19,Fyou could tell that it was all hands
OL,20,Fon deck on Saturday."
